short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to calculate selector performance percentage.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Selector Performance Calculator is a handy Chrome extension that helps warehouse workers and managers accurately calculate selector performance percentages. By inputting the start time, meeting duration, lunch break, and selection time, this extension provides a straightforward way to determine productivity levels. Ideal for managing shift efficiency and optimizing warehouse operations.
